# Bedo Transportation — Ride & Medical Courier Services Website

A fully custom website built from scratch for Bedo Transportation, a DFW-based ride and medical courier service company.

## Project Overview

Designed and developed a professional service website to establish an online presence for a local transportation business offering both standard ride services and medical courier/non-emergency medical transport (NEMT) services.

## Features

- Service overview pages for ride services and medical courier offerings
- Contact and booking section for client inquiries
- Mobile-responsive layout
- Clean, professional design suited for healthcare-adjacent clientele

